Fangspitzen Bundled Tools
---------------------------

1) add-user.sh
	This will add a new unix user and set it up with rtorrent and rutorrent.

2) cron-delete.sh
	Cron script to empty contents of a folder on a user defined amount of days.

3) ftp-backup.sh
	Compress and send a folder over ftp.

4) launchpad-update.sh
	Scans all sources.list and adds their signing key to the system.

